Title: On Some Aspects of Linear Connections in Noncommutative Geometry
Author: Andrzej Sitarz
Comments: LaTeX, 18 pages
Report-no: TPJU 4/95
\\
We discuss two concepts of metric and linear connections in noncommutative
geometry, applying them to the case of the product of continuous and discrete
(two-point) geometry.
